# G endpoint

Add a REST endpoint to an existing controller + register the route.

1. Ask the user for `<Resource> <METHOD> <path>` (e.g.
   `Order POST /orders/{id}/archive`).
2. Run `gofasta g endpoint <args> --dry-run --json` to preview.
3. Surface the controller/service/route changes.
4. Re-run without `--dry-run` to apply if approved.
5. Run `gofasta swagger` after to refresh OpenAPI docs.
